#[ PROFESSIONAL EXPERIENCE #]---------------------------------------------------
printf "Usage: $IN <opts>\n" && head $IN | grep '\$' | cut -d$ -f2 | cut -d# -f1
#=  I11 Industries LLC, On Tour. 
#+    Founder, CEO, CTO, Sept 2010 - Sept 2013.
#-      * Developed cloud-based infrastructure for in-house management of tour 
#--         planning, project tracking, customer relations, marketing, product 
#--         development, manufacturing delivery, financial modeling, and sales 
#--         analysis.
#-	 * API integration in Bash and Python connecting services from          
#--         EventBrite, Google Calendar & Maps, GMail, Twilio, Twitter, and    
#--         more on an AWS-hosted CentOS backend.
printf "\nOf course there are help, debug, and output options:\n\n"
#=  HackFriday.com, Amsterdam, NL. 
#+    Founder, Dev Ops, Prod Ops, System Admin, Nov 2012.	
#-      * Ran DevOps & ProdOps on AWS to build a responsive node.js-based      
#--         RSS-reader for Black Friday streams from hackerspaces worldwide. 
