#=  University of Oklahoma, Norman, OK. 
#+    Research Assistant, High Energy Physics, 2003-2006
#-      * Ported CERNlib CXERF (Complex Error Function) from FORTRAN to C++.
#-      * Built lightweight multi-host data synchronization and 
#--         archival/versioning automations based on rsync. 
